AN unknown man was found near a river, badly injured with gunshot
wounds and he was unable to talk as one of the bullets was still lodged in his mouth.Police spokesperson Colonel Moatshe Ngoepe said  members of the community responded to a request
from the police, asking for assistance in finding a person with gunshot wounds
to contact the Police.

